  "logNo": "223063809915",
  "title": "요즘 유행하는 입간판, 철재 배너에 대해서",
  "date": "2023-04-04",
  "addDate": "2023. 4. 4.",
  "categoryNo": "42",
  "category": "쿡더디자인?!",
  "source_url": "https://m.blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223063809915",
  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-325f47e5-1ea6-44f1-86e5-084b427803e7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-919c023f-50b8-4b53-b532-7a20a9fef4b5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5bf1b584-285d-4fdb-8f25-f1f1b2ceab88\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-7bc11447-1494-42c2-a3d5-de2feafbe935\" style=\"\">철재 배너는 강합니다. 그래서 튼튼하고 외부 바람에 잘 버틸 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c492e588-0214-47f0-bfbf-f31a16c49fb3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bd3f712e-06a0-4dc1-b04a-c6aa23cf5f6d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-553cee56-4ef6-421b-a4e6-f5a27643c919\" style=\"color:#555555;\">요즘 외부에 설치되는 철재 배너를 보면 일반적인 물통이 있는 배너보다는 철재로 구성된 배너를 은근히 많이 볼 수 있습니다. 물론 배너가 실외에 있다 보니 파손이나 손괴가 자주 발생하여 거의 1년 이상을 사용하지 못하는 경우도 많지만 철재 배너는 조금은 튼튼하고 특히 바람에 잘 버틸 수 있는 튼튼한 구조라서 많이 선호하시는 것 같습니다. 이 철재 배너는 하단에 바퀴를 달아서 이동하게 만들 수도 있고 배너를 스프링으로 단단하게 잡아주기 때문에 바람에도 은근히 유동적을 잘 버텨주는 특징이 있습니다. 또한 물통을 별도로 구매하여 버팀목을 추가하여 작업할 수도 있고 산단 하단 프레임이 나사로 단단히 고정되어 있어서 더욱 튼튼한 측면이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line3\" id=\"SE-972a0d7b-7a2e-4fd8-b8aa-2c1aaa878d27\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line3 se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-244444c9-9729-4de5-afbc-326525a3e4aa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c2c5b756-b680-468b-ab84-ad7774c6a886\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-97c4af60-6bbf-4810-9f34-dea06ea50c63\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>철재 배너의 기본 구성은 다음과 같습니다. 기본적으로는 뼈대에 해당하는 프레임과 고무로 만들어진 발 그리고 스피링과 연결 볼트, 아일렛입니다. 다만 물통과 바퀴는 추가 선택사항입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-097414b5-8be0-4df6-9182-9e1021ac4594\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-28cba7f7-1131-437b-9191-593c607c0dd0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3882274f-b48f-4103-8fcf-db2e6175802c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-715fa5f7-2735-4cd7-91d7-d542944c047d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">1. </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-722d2c97-8df1-4006-94aa-c5fc6984ce25\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>프레임</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2c1c5a46-88a1-4b45-a7d0-a58158a2007a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 프레임은 상단과 하단 그리고 밑부분에 해당하는 베이스 프레임으로 나눠집니다. 그리고 상단, 하단을 연결하는 볼트가 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8a4fb47b-f294-4af0-a87b-7032af1953fb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-720fe1c0-5cfe-42a5-8495-6ac019cf0fa6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-872a22e8-9d36-46ed-9b48-e5e75b4d29d5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3e50fcb9-2d50-4d14-bc46-d25c35d8a7c4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f75ddcf-0bb6-429e-a2f8-32420c0cf0f2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-acc58e4d-628c-447c-88b5-4dd8eab6557a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d70086bc-2e50-459d-9837-95938799080f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-60ef2d96-3a25-423f-b96b-310ae1a3b8d4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-834c644c-7390-461d-a67f-03f07c7d4b29\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4d73178-9bfb-4567-9889-f63fb0537d0f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-855eaeb4-df6b-4845-94b3-44e6e047b786\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-51af525e-4cd0-4155-b845-8db87110571f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2ce8850f-e70e-4b03-be98-96e87b763da5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7c33c50d-dac2-43c1-97f8-e22cc6722f34\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0594fd63-71f2-477d-85b6-ba5c5bd267e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">2. 출력물과 프레임과의 연결 : 출력물과 프레임은 스프링으로 연결하도록 구성이 되어 있습니다. 이는 일반적인 고리보다는 더 튼튼하고 바람이나 기타 움직임에 더욱 강하게 대처가 가능합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-267714dd-c34a-46d3-b7ec-3661c6cf2444\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e14164f-3f5b-4e18-9573-9f015d3a726a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-d10d206d-dfcc-48a7-a790-24bad4f6dbc1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e0a94560-3f4f-4107-b5af-0418dc7201ae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2bf8d909-f90e-42f8-844e-560d65168f65\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d9e29901-4be9-431f-81cc-f8ffbb8da159\" style=\"color:#555555;\">3. 기타 구성은 볼트와 물통입니다. 물통은 별도 구매 품목이며 중간에 지지대를 추가할 수 있습니다. 또한 바퀴를 추가할 수 있습니다. 바퀴를 추가하시면 이동이 쉽고 설치 후 바퀴를 제거하여 고정할 수도 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7fefa02c-5768-4315-bb4d-390f6ec8b327\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5cded1de-7a42-4e66-9d9c-8476ebd5fa2a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59fcf57e-c1eb-4d83-a7c3-e91002cf1915\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db263558-287b-430b-be89-692caf2ca04d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-27c3fb1c-4730-454a-a4ff-7fb588c7bba3\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-405c4846-da37-4ace-a51a-d9e3299728ff\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-66076ca5-4488-4375-b47b-90d581dcc451\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:664px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-04ccfe3a-e91e-433c-90f3-dc26c95f6e49\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-15a81570-389a-4f1c-b186-073e3b0c2552\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-097f2670-c342-466d-a3e3-87f36b15a064\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-7cc71190-d4b4-4b1e-b152-c71e3137e354\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223063809915/009.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e539cb8e-9dd7-4d2e-91dd-571b61f01639\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2709444d-d181-4dc5-9b0c-0a2c10661231\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>철재 배너는 이런 분께 유용합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fcad49ed-1793-44fc-80d0-bee81e055421\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9d0cb952-f254-4ca3-b54e-2b86eeeeca73\" style=\"color:#555555;\">기본적으로 일반 실외 배너보다는 튼튼한 구성으로 제작되어 있습니다. 보통 물통과 연결이 약해 쑤러지거나 하는 경우 철재의 강한 프레임이 지탱을 해주므로 조금 더 안전하게 배너를 지지해 줄 수 있습니다. 특히 바람이 많이 부는 해안가나 기타 산간 지역에서 구멍이 나있는 매쉬배너 출력물과 함께 사용하시면 조금은 더 안정적으로 세워둘 수 있습니다. 또한 물통과 지지대를 추가하시면 더욱 잘 버티는 배너로 활용이 가능하십니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-12cd14b0-bb11-4614-a312-51465376ba68\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c7baf470-03ab-45fc-afc9-75e900ec6f9d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cfd64ea5-19ed-4120-91a6-a88a9a4f2f43\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-532c1b2f-85be-45a4-bec0-3f3734843214\" style=\"color:#555555;\">출력물도 스프링으로 프레임과 연결이 되어 있고 철재 프레임에 구멍이 나 있고 스피링 연결이라서 이 부분도 매우 튼튼하게 구성이 되어 있습니다. 그러므로 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumsquare\" id=\"SE-3df9db56-68ab-4c6e-a4d8-f0366deb577a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#badf98;\"><b>철재 배너는 일단 튼튼함을 기본으로 제작되어 있어서 튼튼한 배너를 원하시는 분께 추천</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8290a6b2-b7fc-4313-9471-51a98434d50e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e054aa0-ada4-4197-920d-38d27e975942\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b916b81a-57ec-42cd-a197-64238381cb3b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4aab005c-cd13-419e-b482-291e44bc63a7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cab5b249-87a0-40b6-8d95-42a59d2b5ba8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-01c70e70-5387-4a10-85b0-24782aef0a99\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumsquare se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e6e1bd41-d1dd-4312-bf12-c7babb6f0bdf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}